<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Write User</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h2>간단한 정보를 입력해주세요.</h2>
    <div>
        <form method="post" action="/write">
            <div>
                <p>성함</p>
                <input type="text" name="nick"/>
            </div>

            <div>
                <p>삭제할 때 사용할 비밀번호</p>
                <input type="password" name="password" placeholder="0000"/>
            </div>

            <div>
                <p>게시할 내용</p>
                <textarea name="textarea" placeholder="내용을 입력하세요"></textarea>
            </div>

            <button type="reset">리셋</button>
            <button type="submit">제출</button>
        </form>
    </div>
   

    <div>
        <form action="/list">
            <button type="submit">목록 페이지</button>
        </form>
        </div>
</body>
</html>